metadata.name: Confirmations POST /api/v1/emails/confirmations with an oauth token when user was created by the same application when the account is already confirmed when user changed e-mail and has not confirmed it returns http success

sql_query.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM "oauth_access_tokens" WHERE "oauth_access_tokens"."token" = $1 AND "oauth_access_tokens"."id" != $2 LIMIT $3
